Alexander E. Perriello III       
Executive Compensation
As President and Chief Executive Officer, Realogy Franchise Group at REALOGY HOLDINGS CORP, Alexander E. Perriello III        made $2,757,315 in total compensation.  Of this total $600,000 was received as a salary, $562,800 was received as a bonus, $309,990 was received in stock options, $1,278,987 was awarded as stock and $5,538 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


